 This seminar will be on Wednesday (22 May) at 18:30 at the Cornerstone Church at 7 Cowen Ntuli Street, Gholfsig. Dr Johan Smit ensures an evening filled with light-hearted humour and practical advice on family life and parenting. It will completely change your perception on some of the most challenging issues that parents and families face today. Dr. Smit is a dynamic author, speaker and mentor who lives out his passion for people in his ministry. With more than 30 years of experience, Dr Smit has earned the well-deserved reputation of one of South Africa’s leading speakers on Healthy Christian Family and Living. Entrance is free. For more information, call Letanea at 084 840 1532 or send an email to info@cornerstonem.co.za.     Parents frustrated by a lack of space in Middelburg schools Traffic officers to appear in court for corruption #TrafficAlert: Two dead in Kranspoort accidents VIDEO: Two perish after truck jack-knifes • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za